description: Gradlon, a young Pict, is predestined to be the ruler of his clan. From early youth on, he undergoes an extraordinary initiation where he must face, among others, great deprivations, terrible pains, barbaric rituals and even the gods. Scathach the immortal, a witch of the Skye islands and mistress of the great warriors of Bretagne becomes his teacher. At the end of his training, he becomes a Berzerker, the ultimate warrior, devoid of all fear! The treason of his brother and of all his clan and the resulting revenge, will make him a legenderry hero, who will ultimately rule over Ys, the island-state.
name: Verraad

description: Several years after his wife Brawnen was raped and murdered by his own brother Cormak and his companions the gladiator Ambrosius and Urien a treacherous king, Gradlon the Pict gets more and more a taste for vengeance. Left for dead by the murderers, Gradlon was able to save himself and his daughter Ahs. In the following years they lived in dire circumstances, devoid of everything and everybody, and he learned her to hunt and fight as a Pict. The little Ahs is now ready to follow her father in his quest for revenge. They return to the inhabited world in search for his brother Cormak who, in the meantime, has also killed their father...
name: Wraak

description:
Two mysterious teenagers with an invisible patient interrupt Black Jacks quiet time! Worse still, they claim the unseen patient is their mother and that she has a broken neck! Black Jack isn't amused, but as the temperature unnaturally begins to drop and the weather takes on a life of its own, he begins to think the teenagers' claims may be true after all. Also included are Astro Boy, Buddha, and Phoenix!

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: Gone With the Snow Chapter One
  • Buddha Part Four: The Legend of Sebu the Fox Chapter One
  • Phoenix Yamato Chapter Two
  • Black Jack: On A Snowy Night
name: Vol. 69

description:
While Siddhartha's lectures to the deer continue, a fawn falls into an ant nest and Siddhartha himself gets caught in a desperate attempt to save him! Dhepa refuses to help as time runs out, laughing at the mans plight. Will Dhepa's disciples stand by and watch the ants devour them? Or will they rebel? Also included are Astro Boy, Adolf, and Black Jack!

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: Gone With the Snow Chapter Two
  • Buddha Part Four: The Legend of Sebu the Fox Chapter Two
  • Adolf: Days of Infamy Chapter Three
  • Black Jack: Downpour Chapter One
name: Vol. 70

description:
The mysterious headless robot Damdam terrorizes Los Angeles in Astro Boy: The Faceless Robot! After exhausting their resources, the LAPD realizes they can do nothing to stop the robot from his murderous rampage! When Damdam sets his sights on Japan, the country flies into a panic! Can Astro Boy find the criminal robot in time? Also included are Buddha, Adolf, and Black Jack!

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: The Faceless Robot Chapter One
  • Buddha Part Four: Fool's Way Chapter One
  • Ode to Kirihito: Collapse
  • Black Jack: Downpour Chapter Two
name: Vol. 71

description:
A mysterious disease is turning a boy to stone in Black Jack: A Body Turning to Stone! Black Jack flies to Italy to operate on a boy slowly losing his limbs to a nerve disease. But even Black Jack has limits and announces the boy will need an entire body transplant to live! The lack of cadavers for a child his age is wasting precious time! Will the father of our patient take drastic measure to ensure his son lives? Also included are Astro Boy, Buddha, and Phoenix!

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: The Faceless Robot Chapter Two
  • Buddha Part Four: Fool's Way Chapter Two
  • Phoenix Yamato Chapter Three
  • Black Jack: A Body Turning To Stone
name: Vol. 72

description: This issue contains: Avengers (V.4) ##22, 23
This issue contains: Avenging Spider-Man #3 & 4.

A meeting that just had to happen...Sherlock Holmes meets the Phantom of the Opera! Holmes and Watson are called in regarding the terror occurring at a Paris opera house with claims that it is caused by a ghost. Although Holmes dismisses it outright as needing a spiritualist rather than a consulting detective, he agrees to look into it. Unknown to him, Eric, the tortured ghost of the opera house will prove to be more than a ghost and more than an able opponent in a battle of wits with Holmes and Watson. Issue 1: Holmes and Watson listen to the tale of the mysterious ghost that seems to torment a Paris opera house and decide to look into it. When Watson finds himself face to face with the terrifying apparition he suddenly discovers that even a ghost has the ability to kill. Can Holmes save Watson in time? Part 1 of 2.

volume.name: Sherlock Holmes: Adventure of the Opera Ghost
